                    "line": "About time. That boat's been sitting here rotting."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
                    "line": "I'll fix it. You ready to leave?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "mary",
                    "line": "I've been ready for weeks. Just get it running."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "player",
